<br>
<ul id="feed-list" class="leaflet-list">
  <li class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <span class="card-icon">
        <%= image_tag "rakepage_logo_transparent_32x32.png", size: "16x16" %>
      </span>
      <span class="card-label">
        Getting updated
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-title">
      Focus on Relevant Information
    </div>
    <div class="card-content">
      <p>
        In the age of distractions we are drowning in a sea of irrelevance. With Rakepage you take control of what information you consume for your essentials by customizing your news feeds. <strong><%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path %></strong> to add your favorite blogs (RSS feeds) and/or subreddits from Reddit.com.
      </p>
    </div>
  </li>
  <br>
  <li class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <span class="card-icon">
        <%= image_tag "rakepage_logo_transparent_32x32.png", size: "16x16" %>
      </span>
      <span class="card-label">
        Getting reminded
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-title">
      Remember your Inspirations
    </div>
    <div class="card-content">
      <p>
        Save inspirational content from your personalized news feed to make sure it shows up again in your essentials view. This guarantees that you don't forget about it and you'll take some action.
      </p>
    </div>
  </li>
</ul>
<br><br><br>
<% if !user_signed_in? %>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path,
                  { data: { disable_with: "<i class='fa fa-spinner white'></i> See you soon!"},
                  class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg centered",
                  id: "sign-up" } %>
      <br><br>
      <p class="rake-links info-text centered">
        or <%= link_to "sign in", new_user_session_path %>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
